# Managed authoritative DNS nameservers — example file.
# Copy this file to authoritative_dns_nameservers.conf and replace with your
# organisation's authoritative DNS NS hostnames.
# authoritative_dns_nameservers.conf is listed in .gitignore to avoid leaking
# sensitive internal infrastructure identifiers.
#
# One nameserver per line. Lines starting with # are comments.

# --- Example (Company) ---
# ns1.company.tld
# ns2.company.tld
# ns3.company.tld
# ns4.company.tld
